flowchart LR
    Query["Task query"] --> Retrieval["1. Retrieval\nfetch 20–50 candidates\nrecall first"]
    Retrieval --> Rerank["2. Reranking\nscore for task relevance\nkeep top 5–10"]
    Rerank --> Compress["3. Compression\nextract only task-related sentences"]
    Compress --> Final["Precise retrieved context\nsmall enough to fit, strong enough to guide"]

    Retrieval --> Noise["Raw documents\nmostly irrelevant text"]
    Noise --> Drift["Reasoning drifts when noise stays in context"]

    style Query fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1976d2
    style Retrieval fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ef6c00
    style Rerank fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#7b1fa2
    style Compress fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#388e3c
    style Final fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#f9a825
    style Drift fill:#ffebee,stroke:#c62828
